      <title>房屋建筑商称买家暂停购房，导致 D.R. Horton 股价暴跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-29/d-r-horton-plunges-as-homebuilder-says-buyers-taking-a-pause</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在该房屋建筑商 D.R. Horton Inc. 公布其第四财季业绩令人失望且暗示负担能力挑战阻碍了买家后，该公司股价出现四年多来最大跌幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-29/d-r-horton-plunges-as-homebuilder-says-buyers-taking-a-pause</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 29 Oct 2024 14:13:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
